The paper focuses on commonsense knowledge acquisition and reasoning, which is a core topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions resolving ambiguity, which is a common challenge in knowledge representation (cs.KR). Finally, the paper evaluates the effectiveness of the proposed models through experiments, which is a common practice in information retrieval (cs.IR).
